{"履修期": "通年", "主な教授言語": "日本語", "授業目的": "この授業の目的は、受講生が自らのテーマに関する体系的な研究を行うことにある。", "到達目標": "学術論文を作成する。", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "演習Seminar", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">【スタートアップウィーク】</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">オンライン授業（同時双方向型）／《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">90</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">分》研究計画</span></p>", "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size:11.0224px;\">【事前学習】事前にオンライン授業の準備をする（<span lang=\"EN-US\">75</span>分<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p><span style=\"font-size:11.0224px;\">【事後学習】オンライン授業で出された課題に取り組む（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0224px;\">75</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0224px;\">分）</span>）"], "授業計画1": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">【コアウィークス①～㉔】</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">対面授業／《<span lang=\"EN-US\">2160</span>分》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">90</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">分×<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>回</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">受講者に研究発表をしてもらい、受講者全員で議論する。</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">また、受講生の研究トピックに関連する文献の研究も行う。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\"><br /></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">【フレックスアワーズ①～⑤】</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">対面授業／《<span lang=\"EN-US\">450</span>分》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10pt;\">90</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">分×<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>回</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">履修生と日時を調整して、コアウィークスと同様に演習を行う。</span></p>", "授業外学習2": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">授業外でも、博士論文に向けた研究を行うこと。（週平均<span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span>分以上）</span></p>"}, "評価": {"学位授与の方針との関連Relationship to Diploma 